fs. Firetree's Familiar Augment needs to be improved. Casting this buff on my familiar in a place like ToV is a waste of mana. Even with this buff on, my familiar does not last long at all against a mob's AE. I am not asking for an overpowering spell. I am asking for the spell to have some useability.<br><br>3) Improve &quot;Improved Familiar&quot;. It is wonderful that the familiar is resistant to most forms of magic. As well it should be, but please add at least the same mana regen effect ( +4/ per tick ) as  Greater Familiar. Improved Familiar is described in the game as an &quot;upgrade&quot; to Greater Familiar. An upgrade implies that the effect should have at least all the same effects as the previous version of the spell as well as upgrades to spell resistance, speed, mana reserve, and/or mana regeneration.<br><br>Thanks for reading.<br><br>Inhibin Tucross<br>Sorcerer<br>Saryrn <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udanenel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Danenel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/1/02 1:23:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14979.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What I want the familiar spell to be</span><hr size=1> Familiars are currently unacceptable to me as I continually have problems not being able to target a mob that is hitting me as I keep selecting flappy instead. It's a freaking deathtrap for me and others who acknowledge the same problem.<br><br>I never use familiars now, a single death isn't worth it.<br><br><br> <p><HTML><center><table border=0 bgcolor="0x000000"><tr>	<td><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=42796">	<img width="440" height="110" border=0 align="left" src="http://www.h